# Development methodology

## Communication with client

- Completed at phased intervals
- Basic feedback on the system
- On going concurrent development and design
- Integrated the ongoing research into the design

##Â Prototyping

- Horizontal and vertical prototyping. 
- Vertical prototyping used for the task features
- Horizontal prototyping used for: events, user management, user creation, profile updating
- Prototype in nature, to flesh out ideas and possibilities using the technology

## Functional programming

- Principles of functional programming were used throughout the project
- Usage of currying and partial application to reduce code redundancy


## Creation of plugins

- Throughout the process plugins were created and open sourced
- Percentagebar plugin on Github, allow community collaboration over components if necessary

